metadata.name: Tropix Genesis Culmination Piece: 2013-2022
metadata.description: The 10 year culmination piece brings together the journey I took discovering myself as an independent artist, DJ, & creator as I found my love for music.  Each year was significant in building out my path as it shows the growth I had as a person through the mistakes which turned into learning experiences, the ups and downs of successes & failures, and moments I truly will never forget. As I look ahead, my past will never change, the memories will always exist, every story will be told, & the impact I want to make will continue to push the boundaries of whatâ€™s possible in this space.
